WEBVTT

00:08:27.529 --> 00:08:30.664
they do not look like they have
a lot in common, do they?

00:08:30.688 --> 00:08:32.714
But start seeing their ceiling.

00:08:32.738 --> 00:08:34.876
They have a plastic shield and grass.

00:08:35.512 --> 00:08:37.867
They have the same kind of sofa,

00:08:37.891 --> 00:08:40.721
they store their grain in similar ways,

00:08:41.243 --> 00:08:43.095
they're going to have fish for dinner,

00:08:43.119 --> 00:08:46.447
and they're boiling their water
in identical ways.

00:08:46.471 --> 00:08:49.354
So if we would visit any of these homes,

00:08:49.378 --> 00:08:53.118
there's a huge risk
that we would say we know anything

00:08:53.142 --> 00:08:57.458
about the specific way you do things
in China or Nigeria,

00:08:57.482 --> 00:09:00.087
while, looking at this,
it's quite obvious --